snippet.title: Today Jeremy Corbyn came to #Hastings, Amber Rudd's seat and met Hastings and Rye Labour candidate
snippet.description:
Today Jeremy Corbyn came to #Hastings, Amber Rudd's parliamentary constituency and met Hastings and Rye Labour Party candidate Peter Chowney for Hastings & Rye

In the last General election Peter only lost to Amber Rudd by 346 votes!

Amber Rudd is responsible for UNIVERSAL CREDIT. Since it was introduced in Hastings, there has been an increase in use of food banks of 106%!!

#ScrapUniversalCredit #EnoughIsEnough #GeneralElectionNow ❌
